1. Sections are used to seperate sections If we want an entire page view, use 100vh
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>title</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
  </head>
  <body>
  <section class="first">
      <div class="main">
          <h1>hello</h1>
      </div>
  </section>
  <section class="second">
      
  </section>
  
  </body>
</html>

2. CSS
*{
    margin: 0;
}
.first{
    height: 100vh; 
    background-color: rebeccapurple;
}
.second{
    height: 100vh;
    background-color: cadetblue;
}
